"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae4aa60aa38ef864d4e1a9f8d7fd296c20c37fe","tid":774213,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T18:20:06.000Z","msg":"點解咁轉折，去完上海再去西安？唔直接去西安？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T20:45:10.000Z","msg":"係窮呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西安果邊聽講係唔洗落機<br />\n係架飛機要停係果到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:15:58.000Z","msg":"i see. 只係轉停"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:35:03.000Z","msg":"我錯了真係要轉機<br />\n但唔洗等好耐到到左第二個閘口<br />\n依家係西安<br />\n等轉機<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/093419_d7a8cb86da547bebf4ceb06bab704ade.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F093419_d7a8cb86da547bebf4ceb06bab704ade.png&h=dc2159c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥閪執袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58055c363c06af560c50511ff45d5426d061f233","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:47:31.000Z","msg":"講返係上海<br />\n本黎時間預得好足嘅<br />\n點知排錯隊<br />\n要重新排過<br />\n果條隊多人到仆街<br />\n利用強國特色<br />\n特事特辦同讓領導先走<br />\n成功打尖<br />\n0645起飛<br />\n我0610先寄完倉<br />\n到過檢查嘅時候<br />\n屌你個關員問我有無入藏紙<br />\n我撚有咩<br />\n香港人唔撚要藏紙嫁嘛<br />\n又搞左我5分鐘<br />\n果時已經係0630<br />\n到過安檢嘅時候啦<br />\n比個肥婆由頭摸到落腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過完X-rays 就執埋D嘢跑去上機果到<br />\n如果唔係趕時間我執埋個肥婆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知個閘口係最頭<br />\n跑撚到氣咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/094429_65641e5bcd3bb4a310700a8914afaeca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F094429_65641e5bcd3bb4a310700a8914afaeca.png&h=e53f7912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前面果家人嘅女<br />\n長腳，170，無樣睇，波路ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs 架飛機飛緊嘅時候我唔記得熄鬧鐘，個鬧鐘聲係iphone嘅警報聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇撚死人"},{"pid":"1be4217dddb11dcce82a47243a3c644a86563bb2","tid":774213,"uid":34007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"巴打，我十月都會去西藏阿里，但未夠人包車，可能會報tour，可唔可以推紹下你個團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391bb4d0537a38cb377ae5e31b0b5871bcb1ca6c","tid":774213,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17360990cf4f0e67d1d8a9a846b7fe743d67ee66","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"去左做spa<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/001413_4f4d226f3feef4dfa9d24384ec71583d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F001413_4f4d226f3feef4dfa9d24384ec71583d.png&h=43495d61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次做幾舒服<br />\n同個技師講左好多中港問題<br />\n荼毒下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去之前食左D餃子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/001635_c8cecba20c0532b21d3616dcc232f07e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F001635_c8cecba20c0532b21d3616dcc232f07e.png&h=f82f0e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20大元<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/001904_6c5436ff2b79712da1a57a281979f827.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F001904_6c5436ff2b79712da1a57a281979f827.png&h=9cd5ac4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老尾蟻都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做完spa去先間bar飲左杯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/002045_0f4e39177f23e81e9e92770d384095b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F002045_0f4e39177f23e81e9e92770d384095b3.png&h=c8cb0082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有博家俊陪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"一Q幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d65cb08c4d0227f1cfefbfd32def21326ff4bfe","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1be4217dddb11dcce82a47243a3c644a86563bb2","tid":774213,"uid":34007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"巴打，我十月都會去西藏阿里，但未夠人包車，可能會報tour，可唔可以推紹下你個團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"我係經熟人報，大約係7000到8000左右啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa3423247a26e6ece9c68650b18fa4f30a3ab86","tid":774213,"uid":9763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"成個trip幾多日？<br />\n都係join團？<br />\n洗費幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nplan緊單棍去跟團定自由行好"},{"pid":"2c5c1a936158766d0f9db1f157c35185dc5a796d","tid":774213,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:44:57.000Z","msg":"機票香港網站買?<br />\n大陸網站香港人好似買唔到,幾$張?<br />\n通常見人都係昆明/成都/西安 轉快好多"},{"pid":"a6d0373f4ed3e78d2cd0c1fb5f5cfaaef1ff0222","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa3423247a26e6ece9c68650b18fa4f30a3ab86","tid":774213,"uid":9763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"成個trip幾多日？<br />\n都係join團？<br />\n洗費幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nplan緊單棍去跟團定自由行好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:56:45.000Z","msg":"27號返香港<br />\n自己去拉薩<br />\n再係拉薩報團<br />\n你預返有嘢包埋要10000到12000左右<br />\n當然呢個係比較高嘅價錢<br />\n有D團就係2000幾就有得出發<br />\n但就會變左15個人果D車<br />\n比我嘅感覺係咩人都有<br />\n坐得唔舒服<br />\n所以我會比貴少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aabbfcb09539302546e8af39ef02522d23ff2ff","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5c1a936158766d0f9db1f157c35185dc5a796d","tid":774213,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:44:57.000Z","msg":"機票香港網站買?<br />\n大陸網站香港人好似買唔到,幾$張?<br />\n通常見人都係昆明/成都/西安 轉快好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:57:42.000Z","msg":"都係上網買炸<br />\n4000到5000左右<br />\n要轉機"},{"pid":"61578e442aa84d9c5e77f0e37f927262f2872700","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"琴晚下晝<br />\n西安飛拉薩<br />\n坐我隔離係一個香港女仔<br />\n佢就同佢家姐係拉薩見面3個女仔玩7日<br />\n因爲我都比人放左飛機<br />\n咁咪膽粗粗問下佢我join唔join得囉<br />\n佢又話ok<br />\nPs 正當職業，眉清目秀，靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗住落機一齊去市中心<br />\n點知係攞行李果時我同第二班人吹水<br />\n個行程玩15日<br />\n更加啱我<br />\n咁咪同香港女仔話我跟佢地<br />\n有緣再見啦<br />\n<br />\n點知我行李出左小小問題<br />\n搞左一輪發現<br />\n香港女仔唔見左<br />\n第二班人都唔見埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲好天真咁等左半個鐘最後自己去左市中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/090955_8f11ee4069760b91f7ca476d3896e17a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F090955_8f11ee4069760b91f7ca476d3896e17a.png&h=fd5c9d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/091247_2f8642ddb047bceab3a919058398f239.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F091247_2f8642ddb047bceab3a919058398f239.png&h=4a68832b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琴日真係好多變數搞到個人好攰<br />\n加上有D頭痛<br />\n今日都應該會休息下先<br />\n<br />\n聽日會去阿里地區果到玩<br />\n聽講果邊天氣唔係幾好<br />\n所以都唔會有太大希望"},{"pid":"dfbb21135550d1651ad07c36c7c299a395bdc368","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/121749_11110bd17166cf3ebb03e6dabf25422b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F121749_11110bd17166cf3ebb03e6dabf25422b.png&h=b8863975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叔叔不行了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n血含氧得果69"},{"pid":"10c927e092e83ccb1eb304167ae4835f2d3f1c48","tid":774213,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"保重<br />\n<br />\n高反？"},{"pid":"6d324b3a600fab1923743549aba3052eeb08ba6e","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c927e092e83ccb1eb304167ae4835f2d3f1c48","tid":774213,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"保重<br />\n<br />\n高反？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:22:13.000Z","msg":"小事姐<br />\n一定食到晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b28741207c85c8e058a12c1232e27127e72d70","tid":774213,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"冇買定d紅景天？"},{"pid":"6e1ef4f46cced0f0eb19844cf8a45fc0be4f55ad","tid":774213,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d324b3a600fab1923743549aba3052eeb08ba6e","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c927e092e83ccb1eb304167ae4835f2d3f1c48","tid":774213,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"保重<br />\n<br />\n高反？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:22:13.000Z","msg":"小事姐<br />\n一定食到晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944e06a83e942e43017b34d7b12b8125b8d06263","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7b28741207c85c8e058a12c1232e27127e72d70","tid":774213,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"冇買定d紅景天？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:01:25.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"b25dffb679c858fe7808e23a842766c3fcfba592","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"睇完醫生依好左好多<br />\n依家係布達拉宮觀景台<br />\n好多人<br />\n仲有唔少人攞50蚊出黎影<br />\n我應該會等去日落先走<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/180149_1d1ee3639de6b1c06f5739de2e5cc227.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F180149_1d1ee3639de6b1c06f5739de2e5cc227.png&h=0ee3861b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日全日都係靠得力素同朱古力吊命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1d0bbac461a689360753a6c7b652bd77514caa","tid":774213,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7b28741207c85c8e058a12c1232e27127e72d70","tid":774213,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"冇買定d紅景天？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"呢d野冇用既，如果得洗撚吸氧氣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e5f8ee2a744680e77a2be3d416e858ba340eb5","tid":774213,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9cc172010338b4bea3d73e4889c5c35f72779cec","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T11:09:51.000Z",