.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紅景天係無用ga, 之前睇blog, 西藏D導遊/司機介紹另一隻...唔記得係乜, 仲笑紅景天只係普通健康藥, 對高山反應完全無用"},{"pid":"c3bc9be99627182fc2b845f14a8cfdd4ff41e117","tid":774213,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"下禮拜到我出發<br />\n<br />\n想問下西藏而家天氣點<br />\n夜晚幾多度倒，係咪好凍？駛唔駛帶羽絨？<br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe9ecfa0a1cd8e49ee16bd9f2d2c5d06af0226f","tid":774213,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74b7561cfa90af998240c3542ed8671bde142966","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f1d0bbac461a689360753a6c7b652bd77514caa","tid":774213,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7b28741207c85c8e058a12c1232e27127e72d70","tid":774213,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"冇買定d紅景天？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"呢d野冇用既，如果得洗撚吸氧氣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"我都覺得冇咩用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"唔食 diamox?"},{"pid":"c93b2d193e8fcb0b87f1584334e90ff487fc4b5d","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba445f8a876cc85a6680e29d0ba86a3b97cd9b4","tid":774213,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74b7561cfa90af998240c3542ed8671bde142966","tid":774213,"uid":100467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f1d0bbac461a689360753a6c7b652bd77514caa","tid":774213,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"呢d野冇用既，如果得洗撚吸氧氣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"我都覺得冇咩用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"